 <div class="postConteudo"><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt"><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;color: #333333;font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&amp;quot">- <a title="O MANIFESTO DAS BESTAS CÚBICAS" href="http://veja.abril.com.br/blog/reinaldo/geral/o-manifesto-das-bestas-cubicas/"><span style="text-decoration: none"><span style="color: #0000ff">O MANIFESTO DAS BESTAS CÚBICAS;<br />
